Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an4\fs150\fsp13\fn@思源黑体 medium\bord3.5\b1\c&H3A4829&\3c&HFFFDFE&\frz270\2c&H00FFFF&\2a&HFF&\clip(18.67,82,274.67,98)\t(0,397,\clip(19.2,80,88.8,284.8))\t(1023,1941,\clip(19.2,80,88.8,580))\pos(72,84.77)}觀察{\fn@Source Han Sans medium}？{\fn@思源黑体 medium} 觀察什麼{\fn@Source Han Sans medium}？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.18,0:07:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 你說二號街的超市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.10,0:07:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她想做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.00,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,特工之間應該避免不必要的接觸
